2004-05-12 Jordi Mas i Hernandez <jordi@ximian.com>
	* bitmap.c, image.c, gdpi.h:
	- Correct support for Format24bppRgb, Format32bppArgb, Format32bppPArgb, 
	Format32bppRgb pixel formats
