	(make_pie): private functions (make_foo) to be reused by DrawFoo
	and FillFoo.
	
	(convert_fill_mode): Converts a GpFillMode to a cairo_fill_rule_t.

	(GdipDrawPie, GdipFillEllipse, GdipFillPolygon): Implemented.

